  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.poster.avif?t=1773855162\" width=1170 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.webm?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.mp4?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/ccb9ca56bdf462603ffa6639115d2fe5.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span><i>Clank!</i>, the iconic deck-building board game adventure, challenges daring thieves to sneak into a dragon’s lair, steal one of her precious artifacts, and escape – before you’re roasted to a crisp!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Winning fans and awards around the world, <i>Clank!</i> is one of the most-beloved modern board games, with a wide range of expansions and adaptations for players to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/c9e394e04b92d427fb10b40dc85873ce.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>The deeper you go, the more valuable treasures you’ll find…but the harder it will be to escape! So be quick and be quiet: One false step and – <i>CLANK!</i> Each careless sound risks drawing the dragon’s attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re competing against your fellow thieves to claim the most valuable prize…but you can only enjoy your loot if you make it out of the depths alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/1275ac5f06dafc1eb947df8a80428a13.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>You’ll need a good pair of boots, a sharp sword, and all your roguish skills to survive in the dungeon. Along the way, you’ll acquire new items, abilities, and allies that will help you achieve victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blending deck-building and exploration, <i>Clank!</i> offers a unique dungeon-delving adventure each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/f96bd21c05066de2c78ccbf52a378695.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>Learn the ropes in a guided Tutorial, then hone your abilities by collecting Achievements and completing Challenges. Play cross-platform against friends, or compete in exciting new Heists that put you up against players from around the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However you choose to enter the dungeon: Good luck!...you’re going to need it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc81059b14337a.poster.avif?t=1773855162\" width=1170 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc81059b14337a.webm?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc81059b14337a.mp4?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.poster.avif?t=1773855162\" width=1170 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.webm?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/602e984ddae26c846ae74288d10013b0.mp4?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/ccb9ca56bdf462603ffa6639115d2fe5.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span><i>Clank!</i>, the iconic deck-building board game adventure, challenges daring thieves to sneak into a dragon’s lair, steal one of her precious artifacts, and escape – before you’re roasted to a crisp!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Winning fans and awards around the world, <i>Clank!</i> is one of the most-beloved modern board games, with a wide range of expansions and adaptations for players to enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/c9e394e04b92d427fb10b40dc85873ce.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>The deeper you go, the more valuable treasures you’ll find…but the harder it will be to escape! So be quick and be quiet: One false step and – <i>CLANK!</i> Each careless sound risks drawing the dragon’s attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re competing against your fellow thieves to claim the most valuable prize…but you can only enjoy your loot if you make it out of the depths alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/1275ac5f06dafc1eb947df8a80428a13.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>You’ll need a good pair of boots, a sharp sword, and all your roguish skills to survive in the dungeon. Along the way, you’ll acquire new items, abilities, and allies that will help you achieve victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blending deck-building and exploration, <i>Clank!</i> offers a unique dungeon-delving adventure each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/f96bd21c05066de2c78ccbf52a378695.avif?t=1773855162\" width=600 height=70 /></span>Learn the ropes in a guided Tutorial, then hone your abilities by collecting Achievements and completing Challenges. Play cross-platform against friends, or compete in exciting new Heists that put you up against players from around the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However you choose to enter the dungeon: Good luck!...you’re going to need it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc81059b14337a.poster.avif?t=1773855162\" width=1170 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc81059b14337a.webm?t=1773855162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722870/extras/02fac9bf7b56300fb8dc